1.5
log
@Delete an accidentally duplicated "Libs.private" line in the .pc file which was
causing "pkgconfig libiodbc --exists" to return false with a knock-on effect
of triggering a different codepath in php's autoconf script causing it to link
the main binary against libiodbc. PHP problem reported by naddy.
@
text
@$OpenBSD: patch-admin_libiodbc_pc_in,v 1.4 2014/09/16 15:01:48 sthen Exp $
--- admin/libiodbc.pc.in.orig	Tue Apr 15 12:00:45 2014
+++ admin/libiodbc.pc.in	Tue Sep 16 14:29:16 2014
@@@@ -88,6 +88,6 @@@@ Name: iODBC
 Description: @@PACKAGE_NAME@@
 Version: @@PACKAGE_VERSION@@
 Requires:
-Libs: -L${libdir} -liodbc -liodbcinst @@LIBADD_DL@@
+Libs: -L${libdir} -liodbc -liodbcinst
 Libs.private: -lpthread
 Cflags: -I${includedir}
@


